Title: Man Up
Plot: The CSIs question the validity of an online picture depicting a murdered call girl until they find the same woman strangled to death in the dumpster that appears in the photo.
GuestStars: Carrot Top, Rich Sommer, Kevin Weisman, Amy Acker, James Snyder, Jonathan Chase, Alex Carter, Archie Kao, Sheeri Rappaport, Trevor Donovan, Blake Gibbons
